                  <ul>
                    <li>Our Colors: Black and Gold</li>
                    <li>Our Motto: "Seek virtue and knowledge"</li>
                    <li>Previously known as the Pioneers, the school's teams were renamed the Golden Grizzlies in 1998.</li>
                    <li>Forbes National Academic Ranking: 528</li>
                    <li>Although many of Oakland's students commute from surrounding areas, there are more than 3,000 who live
